Package jromp.parallel.var

Class ReductionVariable<T extends Serializable>

java.lang.Object
jromp.parallel.var.ReductionVariable<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the variable.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Variable<T>
public class ReductionVariable<T extends Serializable> extends Object implements Variable<T>
Represents a reduction variable that its value is reduced from private variables using a reduction operation.
